item.title: Failed to open a session for the virtual machine Whonix-Gateway-XFCE
item.dc:creator: Lilias
item.description:
Just as the error message states, you have AMD-v disabled in the bios. Go into the bios settings and enable anything to do with virtualization. The setting to enable may be called SVM.

Read full topic

item.dc:creator: Cloudsvengeance
item.description:
It is my first time using Whonix I followed your instructions for downloading VBox and whonix, Imported into VBox and for both Gateway and Workstation I get the Error message “Failed to open a session for the virtual machine” I will provide logs for you. I am useing VBox 6.0 and Whonix 15.0.03.3. Thank you.
